div.stage:
Enter Ate as before. Then let their follow Omphale daughter to the king of Lydia, hauing a club in her hand, and a lions skinne on her back, Hercules following with a distaffe. Then let Omphale turn about, and taking off her pantofle, strike Hercules on the head, then let them depart. Ate remaining, saying; 

Quem non Argolici mandata seuera Tyranni, 

Non potuit Iuno vincere, vicit amor.
